{"tid":582504,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"1705 賓仕國際 討論區","createTime":"2018-03-06T08:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T01:09:06.000Z","uid":10606,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"938a4cce08ebe42496b4f1acaaedcb0ce7336cf7","tid":582504,"uid":10606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:36:57.000Z","msg":"智通財經APP獲悉，香港「天仁茗茶」經營商及日本「味覺糖」糖果分銷商賓仕國際(01705)已於今日中午截止公開發售。有市場消息透露，出現逾<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2000倍超額認購</strong></span>，有望打入香港史上超購最多新股三甲之內。<br />\n<br />\n智通財經早前文章《買股還是買茶?賓仕國際(01705)手握網紅茶飲店登陸港股》中提到，得益於旗下零售品牌奶茶店天仁茗茶的持續火爆，近3年來賓仕國際整體的營收穩步增長，從2015年到2017年截至3月31日止年度收益2.83億港元、3億港元、3.68億港元，年復合增長率達9.15%。<br />\n<br />\n大家抽左未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abca731a9fa8333d1ab376ab7f7ba2eadf0dfdf0","tid":582504,"uid":59990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"屌 實抽唔到"},{"pid":"2225fabbb25735f6886da0b2ea26a0a095de06b6","tid":582504,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"發達機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a616468c923695b5c772c1dbac7227954b6a53","tid":582504,"uid":10606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"抽左5手 <br />\n覺得5手同50手最多都係一注中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6901364f6cdf9b41ee673d93ca613455af8328","tid":582504,"uid":10606,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T08:40:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">超購2600倍 On 9999</span></span>"},{"pid":"a85e7a1f06a690b6da7432aa3c14736a43f51602","tid":582504,"ui